[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "え……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00672",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "うわあっ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00673",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ちょっとレスナちゃん、なんで止まって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00674",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "あ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00675",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "なに、ここ……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00676",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "空が、広い……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00677",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "星、でかっ……\nあの灰色のほう、いつも見てる大の月……よね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00678",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "でも、あの一際大きくて、青い星は……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00679",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "それよりも……これ！　これも、これも！！！\n全部、マナだ！　純度の高いマナが、こんなに……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00680",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "果ての大陸の伝説は、本当だったんだ！！\nこんな、こんな……っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00681",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "お兄ちゃん？　もしかして泣いてるの……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00682",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ちょっとだけそっとしといてあげて。\n冒険者の本懐、ってやつよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00683",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "う、うん……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00684",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（たどり着いたんだ、果ての大陸に）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00685",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（長い、長い旅だった……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00686",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "8643265264907274754",
		"text": "果ての大陸を見つけて、マナの問題を解決して……。\nみんなが錬金術で幸せになれるようにしたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00687",
		"still_path_hash": "3572566872346296899",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "8643265264907274754",
		"text": "だから立派な錬金術士になって、\n果ての大陸を探しに行きたいと思ってます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00688",
		"still_path_hash": "3572566872346296899",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "私はそれを見つけ出すのが夢なんだ。\nもし果ての大陸が見つかり、マナが発掘されれば……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00689",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "錬金術もきっとまた、大昔のように繁栄する。\nそうすれば便利で楽しい世界になる……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00690",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ザスキア",
		"romanized_name": "Saskia",
		"model_path_hash": "8393915555796547279",
		"text": "レスナ。あなたはこのまま果ての大陸を目指せば\nいいの。私も応援しちゃうわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_050_038_00691",
		"still_path_hash": "3628130916430439847",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "8643265264907274754",
		"text": "錬金術の復興は、私にとっても夢です。果ての大陸を\n目指すことも。でも、師匠に言われたからじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00692",
		"still_path_hash": "3572566872346296899",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "果ての大陸は初耳だなあ。あれ、じゃあレスナたちが\nこの国にはるばるやってきたのって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00693",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はい。果ての大陸を探すためです。\nこの無数島群域に、手掛かりがあると信じて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00694",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それじゃ、「九偉人図」を全部\nくっつけてみるね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00695",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "「九人の偉人、皆がその手を差し伸べしとき\n　汝が前に、果てへの道は開かれん」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00696",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "案内人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "私の問いに答えてください。\n正しく答えられれば、果ての大陸へと案内しましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_723_038_00697",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "大丈夫。自分で見つけ出せばいいんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00698",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ここまでの道だって、\n誰かに案内されて来たわけじゃないんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00699",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ここまで、色んなことがあった。\n　たくさんの人に助けていただいた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00700",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（そしてついに、ついに……たどり着いたんだ！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00701",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "やーーーーーーっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00702",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "わっ。どうしたの、レスナ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00703",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ご、ごめんなさい。\n嬉しい気持ちが溢れてきちゃって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00704",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "アタシも嬉しいから、一緒に叫ぶよ！\nハンマーーーーーー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00705",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "えへへ、ありがとう、イザナちゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00706",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "ねえ、ここが果ての大陸だとしてさ、\n地理的にはどこにあるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00707",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "果ての大陸の伝説では、遥か海の向こうに\nあるって話だった気がするんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_038_00708",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "少なくとも、諸島同盟にこんな景色の島はないね。\nその様子だとランターナのほうにもないんだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00709",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん。ここはいったいどこなんだろう――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00710",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……気になるのは、星です",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00711",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "星……そういえば、\nいつもの星空とは見え方がぜんぜん違う……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00712",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はい。いつも、どこでも見えていた黄金星が見えない。\nそして、見たことがない大きな青い星",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00713",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あの青……見覚えがあります。海の色みたいな深い青。\n白いのは、雲、ですよね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00714",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "えっと、じゃああの大きい緑は……？\n小さい緑が、あっちにポツポツとあるのは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00715",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "地図で見た形だよ。大きい緑はランターナ大陸で、\n小さくてたくさんある緑は無数島群域、だと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00716",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "じゃあ、今アタシたちがいる場所って……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00717",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "果ての大陸は……黄金星のことだったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00718",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……面白いじゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00719",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00720",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 49,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "こんなの、誰も知らなかったわよきっと。\nまあ、あの様子だと、九偉人は知ってたっぽいけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00721",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 50,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "とにかく人類は知らないはず！\nねえ、果ての大陸こと、黄金星を探検しましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_038_00722",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 51,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "そうこなくっちゃ！　すっごい発見をして、\n歴史に天才ヨハナの名を残してやるわ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_038_00723",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 52,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おいおい、何があるか分からないんだ。\n進むにしても慎重に行こうよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00724",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 53,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "理屈で分かっていても、止められないよ。\n冒険者魂ってやつだね。かくいう私も……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00725",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 54,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ここまで来たらどこにいても危険は一緒じゃない？\n退路を確保しつつ進んでみましょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_038_00726",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 55,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "やれやれ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00727",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]